  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nInput validation is 1 character off. Is is not possible to send a message with 2000 characters even though this is a valid input.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Enter 2000 character message and send.\r\n2. Error is given.\r\n3. Enter 1999 character message and send.\r\n4. Message is sent.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nA message at or within the 2000 char limit can be sent.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nA 2000 char message cannot be sent.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50769329/186423501-055f2c85-42f8-4d0c-8d2c-96cb083b00b5.png)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: https://ci.status.im/job/status-desktop/job/platforms/job/macos/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/pkg/StatusIm-Desktop-220824-111243-1c7719.dmg\r\n- Operating System: Mac \r\n\r\n",
